---
layout: layout.njk
title: Blue Quill Studio | Books, Stories & Leadership
description: Books, leadership, stories and technology by Blue Quill Studio.
---

<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="kicker">Official Author Website</span>

    <h1>Blue Quill Studio</h1>

    <p>
      Books • Leadership • Stories • Technology.
      Founded by Syed Tanweer Islam.
    </p>

    <a class="btn" href="/books/">Explore Books</a>
    <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/blog/">Read Blog</a>
  </div>
</header>

<section>
  <h2 class="section-title">Featured Books</h2>

  <div class="grid2">

    <div class="card">
      <img src="/assets/when-we-loved-cover.jpg"
           style="width:100%;border-radius:18px;margin-bottom:20px;">

      <h3>When We Loved in Silence</h3>

      <p>
        A heartfelt story of love, silence, sacrifice,
        family, memory and destiny.
      </p>

      <a class="btn"
         href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0H6K3R9VT"
         target="_blank">
         Buy on Amazon
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="/assets/it-battlefield-cover.jpg"
           style="width:100%;border-radius:18px;margin-bottom:20px;">

      <h3>Years of Lessons from the IT Battlefield</h3>

      <p>
        Practical lessons for IT professionals and
        aspiring leaders.
      </p>

      <a class="btn"
         href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0H61QLYFK"
         target="_blank">
         Buy on Amazon
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2 class="section-title">Latest Blog Posts</h2>

  <div class="grid3">
    {% for post in collections.all | reverse %}
      {% if post.url and post.url.startsWith("/blog/") and post.data.title %}
        <a class="card post-card" href="{{ post.url }}">
          <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          <span class="btn">Read More</span>
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
